en_215609_0	The Court ruling on whether to deport drug kingpin Makandure Madush has been further postponed until May 9 by the Dubai Court.
en_215609_1	Madush filed a motion requesting the court not to deport him from Dubai saying that his life would be at risk in Sri Lanka.
en_215609_2	Meanwhile actor Ryan Van Rooyan who was remanded after being deported by Dubai police was further remanded until May 9th.
en_215609_3	He was produced before the Matara Magistrate today.
en_215609_4	Meanwhile, Amila Prasanna Hettihewa alias Sunshine Suda who was released after being deported by Dubai police was arrested yesterday with 4 grams of heroin in his possession.
en_215609_5	Later, he was produced before the Court and was remanded until May 16.
